面對面認人。控方昨播放認人片段，兩警表現不合作，全程垂頭合上眼，即使曾健超指示警方要求他們「企起身」、「擘大眼」及「望向前」，但兩人無動於衷。安排認人的總督察向曾稱「唔可以逼佢做任何嘢」。<br />\n記者：歐陽聯發<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20161021/19807682\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20161021%2F19807682&d=PKFOq%2F3hdZkIocf411TDxP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=d08cfef8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20161021%2F19807682&h=d6042b5d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20161021/19807682</a>"},{"pid":"71ef76c05ad4a2353ae581104503d52d1b9727b0","tid":541281,"uid":55924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T11:30:04.000Z","msg":"我覺得我地淡左"}]}